@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Search Supplier (Happy Path)
autonumber

actor "Admin/Manager" as User
participant "UI Service" as UI
participant "SupplierController" as Ctrl
participant "SupplierService" as Svc
participant "SupplierRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

User -> UI : Nhập từ khóa tìm kiếm (Tên, Email, SĐT...) và nhấn "Tìm kiếm"
UI -> Ctrl : POST /api/suppliers/GetData\n(SupplierSearch)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc : GetData(search)
activate Svc

Svc -> Repo : GetQueryable()
activate Repo
Repo --> Svc : IQueryable<Supplier>
deactivate Repo

Svc -> Svc : Build Query (Filter by Name, Email, Phone, IsActive)
Svc -> Svc : Select new SupplierDto

Svc -> DB : Execute Query (Pagination)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : List<SupplierDto> & TotalCount
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : Create PagedList<SupplierDto>

Svc --> Ctrl : PagedList<SupplierDto>
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> UI : Ok(ApiResponse<PagedList<SupplierDto>>)
deactivate Ctrl

UI --> User : Hiển thị kết quả tìm kiếm

@enduml